cat << EOF
Xystray is a simple implementation of freedesktop.org systray specification
(a.k.a notification area) for XWindow system. It is meant for use in simple
desktop environments which does not provide such facility by default eg. FVWM.
It may also run under GNOME or KDE but the default tray programme has to be
disabled then.
EOF
